
Porting HWA to ATmega328
========================

File hwa_atmega328_1.h (copied from hwa_attiny84_1.h):
  Define HW_DEVICE_ATMEGA328
  Define HW_DEVICE_FLASHSIZE
  Define HW_DEVICE_EEPROMSIZE
  Define HW_DEVICE_RAMSIZE
  Define HW_DEVICE_NVECTORS
  Define HW_DEVICE_RAMSTART
  Define HW_DEVICE_SIGNATURE
  Include hwa_atmegax8_1.h

File hwa_atmegax8_1.h (copied from hwa_attinyx4_1.h):
  Define HW_DEVICE_ATMEGAX8
  Include "hwa_atmelavr_1.h"
  Include "hwa_atmegax8_..._1.h"
  Define hw_syshz according to HW_DEVICE_FUSE_LB and HW_DEVICE_XSOHZ
  Define HWA_DCL as list of HWA_DCL_...
  Define hw_sleep_until_irq
